tracks.text: 8 TV screens are held by mechanical arms. One screen approaches us, and features a young man with a pencil mustache and goatee.
Another TV shows us a man with highlights holds up his hands with the thumbs sticking out.
A third TV depicts a man with short, spiky blonde hair.
A TV shows a concert for Eiffel 65.
Another shows a space ship flying approaching a planet.
A blue humanoid alien sits on a chair, looking at us through a windshield.
A second blue alien sits next to him.
The first alien watches Eiffel 65 on a screen and presses a red button.
A beam appears below the spaceship. The goatee man sings on stage, jumps, and gets picked up by the a beam. The spiky haired man stares, mouth open.
The aliens fly off. Behind them, the goatee man floats in a glowing orb. The aliens bob their bald heads.
The ship flies away from Earth.
The 2 other band members put on glasses and get into a small, green spaceship.
They fly off, over their audience.
The aliens bob their heads and sing along.
The small ship approaches the alien ship.
It flies by. It's about a quarter the size.
The small ship can be seen through a side window.
The spiky man looks at us and sticks out his tongue.
The small ship chases the larger ship towards a red planet.
The aliens run down a hallway in blue light.
They run past spinning fans as a red light strobes.
The larger ship lands in a hangar.
A hook removes the orb and goatee man, and drops him on a platform. 2 blue men looks up.
The platform floats away. The men follow him.
In the  hallway, the aliens walk in front of the orb.
The small ship lands. The man with highlights jumps out. The aliens fire blue lasers. He dodges. Another alien runs.
The highlights man throws red light orbs out from his hand. 3 aliens fall back. Another alien does a jump kick
The highlights man throws another red orb, and it explodes. An alien falls over the side of the dock.
Aliens wave arms in front of a stage.
The goatee man is carried to the stage.
The orb disappears. The goatee man bounces and sings to us.
TV screen and the text Eiffel 65 flash behind him.
The alien audience waves their arms back and forth.
The goatee man squints his eyes and looks down.
He looks surprised.
4 aliens with guns runs to the spacedock.
The highlights man punches the aliens. One goes flying into a pile of boxes.
The highlights man keeps punching. More aliens go flying.
The spikey man, with a stern expression, runs forward. The highlights man runs through the hallway.
A door opens, and an alien walks through, backlit by a spotlight
The highlights man stands on one foot and readies a glowing orb
The red orb knocks an alien over. 2 more aliens run through the doorway
The highlights man slaps more aliens into the wall
One flies into a fan and spins around with it
The spiky man walks intently down the hallway
Inside a factory, the highlights man does martial arts moves in front of an alien.
The highlight man shoots blue lightning.
The spiky man bops an alien. Another alien approaches, and he holds up a palm. The alien falls backwards.
The highlights man holds up an alien by blue lightning, and swings it around.
The highlights man swings on a rope, grabs the goatee man on stage, and swings away. The small ship flies away, carrying the 3 men.
A sign from the planet approaches them. It has blue text, reading Please Come Back.
The highlights man looks back at the goatee man, who nods. The ship turns around.
The 3 men perform on the alien stage.
An alien dances on stage with them.
The spiky man waves his hands over his head.
The highlights man jumps with a fist in the air, in front of a keyboard.
Fade to black.
